sentences.english: It selects top grade raw materials in the Land of Abundance, and is produced with our advanced techniques.
sentences.chinese: 精选天府之国优质原料，采用盈棚技术精工制作。

sentences.english: Excuse me, how can I get to Tianfu Square?
sentences.chinese: 请问，我怎样才能到天府广场？

sentences.english: Sichuan has always enjoyed the reputation of the being “Heavenly Land of Plenty”.
sentences.chinese: 四川素有“天府之国”的美称。

sentences.english: Szechwan is called the Heavenly Kingdom. There are lots of rich people there.
sentences.chinese: 四川是天府之国，那可富庶得很哪。

sentences.english: Shuntian Prefecture was subordinated by central authority and had no relationship of command with Zhili viceroy.
sentences.chinese: 顺天府由中央直辖，与直隶总督并无统属关系。

sentences.english: Sichuanalso has a nickname, Land of Abundance.
sentences.chinese: 四川还有一个别称，天府之国。

sentences.english: Tianfu card crucible brand has become the most graphite crucible.
sentences.chinese: 天府牌》坩埚成为国内最有品牌的石墨坩埚。

sentences.english: The Yingtian prefecture in Northern Song Dynasty was located in Nanjing, the supplementary capital.
sentences.chinese: 北宋时期的应天府，是陪都南京的所在地。

sentences.english: People listen to the old site of the Tianfu Road, then talk about the glorious ancient town yesterday.
sentences.chinese: 听老人们用地道的天府话讲述古镇辉煌的昨天。
